snippet.title: Claybook Switch Launch Trailer [NA]
snippet.description:
Claybook is now available on Nintendo eShop! https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/claybook-switch

Claybook is a unique physics-based puzzle game in a world made entirely of clay. The game is also available on PC, Xbox One, and PS4.
